Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落惊人的妖气\N朝着丑寅方向消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次出现了既非人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也非妖怪的一个亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  新的战斗马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:16.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:52.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:05.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第102话 被亡魂袭击的妖狼族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向…应该是往这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股巨大不祥的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着丑寅方向飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子这股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的应该就是奈落没错  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这个坏蛋\N到底跑到哪里去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会\N因为结界被犬夜叉给破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只好躲起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这么凶恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会就这样躲起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道什么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落已经发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们追踪到妖气在哪里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以故意布下陷阱\N好引我们上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一路上碰的陷阱够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这么看来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是更接近奈落的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定又有陷阱等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落到底\N又布下了什么样的陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪全都逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  是这股臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在山谷里的窝\N都被歼灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沼泽里的洞穴也被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉鬼接二连三吃了他们兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山上那些妖怪\N有一半都被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利爪跟尖牙全都打不过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对抗这帮侵略者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看非得借助\N四魂之玉碎片才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  那些坏蛋又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山对面那些家伙都被吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在逐渐\N逼近我们的势力范围了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有同伴被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看除了找钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不是他的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次菖蒲想尽办法去求他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道他坚持不肯回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉鬼来了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  我们分头应付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮妖怪为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的食物被厉鬼抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道被厉鬼吃掉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得先喂饱这帮妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快先过河再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到\N厉鬼这么快就下山来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说有一股强大妖气飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从附近打听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是听说又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝哪边飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点大家好像也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺着这条河流一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上游就是北方的山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来到菖蒲\N跟长老爷爷家附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次菖蒲那个丫头说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么厉鬼来  大家有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了命想拉我跟她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却被我给赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有一种很不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长老
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  你振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙已经追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧\N我来做饵引开那帮妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就趁这个机会快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一真追过来  老爷爷不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要保护长老尽快找到钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他回来打败亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区几个杂碎小妖怪\N我还不放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上还有伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧  菖蒲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再婆婆妈妈说这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要辜负老爷爷的一番心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们也是妖狼族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷  原来你会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我恐怕不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是北方山上的长老吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菖蒲特别下山来\N找钢牙少主回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你真的是太好了  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们大家放弃了家园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从北方山上逃到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些妖怪也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到这来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在躲避什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个亡魂\N是从我们势力范围之外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更北的地方来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是妖怪  也不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上发出一股\N尸体跟坟土的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就开始吃…附近的妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下怎么办  钢牙少主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会想去找那个亡魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是正在找奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟我们有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才更要去查个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多兄弟被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够坐视不理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只臭笨狗也朝这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股狗骚味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可受不了被他抢在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大一股狼骚味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股特别自以为是的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙那小子\N八成刚刚走过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来\N钢牙也跟我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正朝着丑寅方向前进是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他是不是\N掌握到其他线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚刚  说了钢牙对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菖蒲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菖蒲姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不就是那个把戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当成情敌的妖狼族姑娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是回北方山上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是回去了  不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有厉鬼追我们的族人\N所以又逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只专门吃鬼的厉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一只专门吃鬼的厉鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果今天不能够翻过这座山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得在野外过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如折回村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求那些村民留我们过一夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听人说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近这一带\N经常有厉鬼出来害人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的碰到厉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候用我的法力\N打鬼给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是鬼在吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父  你快收拾他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意\N既不是妖怪也不是人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怪物\N是从东北方下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东北方?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是丑寅方向了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没多久的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在山里的妖怪  精灵跟鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近甚至逼近\N我们的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大批兄弟都被吃掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们妖狼族\N应该没有这么不堪一击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像一座小山那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会有这种鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说自古以来\N有一些含恨而终的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了替自己报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往往会化身成为厉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是居然把妖怪全部都吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能够唤醒这种厉鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了他还会有谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须带着长老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有仅存的妖狼族兄弟逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果碰见钢牙\N我一定帮你转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族兄弟\N四处逃窜的这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽管放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己小心一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重啊  菖蒲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个亡魂\N会发出尸体跟坟土的臭味喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶骨大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有四魂之玉碎片的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子比他\N那些狼兄弟来得更是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么来着…琥珀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是先留下你背上\N那块四魂之玉碎片再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝你不要随便乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们也在一边虎视眈眈哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我也不想这么快就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费了那么大力气\N好不容易才复活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你对我这班狼兄弟出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上也有\N四魂之玉碎片的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好庞大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片我是要定了\N还有你那条命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的一个怪物喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个什么亡魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼群的老爷爷说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上还真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既不是人  也不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一股尸体跟坟土的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上还有臭味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从坟冢里出来\N已经好一段日子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  他没有否认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真的是亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子我得再多吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增加身上的血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你生得人高马大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来成为\N我凶骨大爷的血肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你这只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别想再吃\N我狼族兄弟的血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脚上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你两只脚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都带有四魂之玉碎片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么凶骨是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怪物身上\N闻不到奈落的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可见他并不是奈落的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点可以确定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什么怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用问也知道我是个人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是\N绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你只是人类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能死后还从坟墓里复活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都要归功于\N这个四魂之玉碎片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是它让我的状况\N比活着的时候更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片!居然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你从什么地方\N弄到这个东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不过是我嘴边的一块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你这种慢吞吞的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为可以抓到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快的家伙是在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想打哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你瞄准一点行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个可恶的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要看看你\N还能够威风多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要每次\N都用同一招行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给我滚回坟墓里去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇快看  那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  为什么会发出\N这么强的光芒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落跟钢牙碰上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  这并不是奈落的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂之玉的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想要打哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧  杂碎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真以为三两下\N就能把我摆平了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙  看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些四魂之玉碎片\N就送给我吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要做梦了  混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不痛不痒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标本来就不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙少主  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制凶骨的  原来是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩一堆白骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为身体里\N被埋入四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能复活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮兄弟们报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不幸遇难的兄弟\N这下可以瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的邪气\N朝着丑寅方向去了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  戈薇是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己小心一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇也跟我说过同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戈薇一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说凶骨已经死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  蛇骨大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那个没用的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙本来就是\N我们之中最差劲的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  怎么样呢  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  这次我的对手犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是不是个帅哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点恐怕要\N请您自己去判断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:34.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:43.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:53.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:24:03.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:20.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:27.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:31.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:38.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.95,0:24:48.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
